Bedel, 1907: 265. Unjustified emendation of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Latreille" authorityYear="1824" class="Hexapoda" family="Carabidae" genus="Calleida" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="826" pageNumber="827" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
